io.pivotal.rti.protocols

Annotation Type ProtocolDetails


  • @Documented
@Inherited
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value={PACKAGE,TYPE})
public @interface ProtocolDetails
    Annotation to let RTI discover new fields contributed through ProtocolAdapter implementations. This is a parent (holder) level annotation that contains individual ProtocolDetail that defines details about each individual fields contributed.

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
